translate russian rjwhitneywarning_0a9be0ab:

    # wt "Yes, it was on the lowest shelf. I think the box second from the right. They might all have gems in them though."
    wt "Да, на самой нижней полке. Кажется, вторая коробка справа. Хотя, возможно, во всех них драгоценные камни."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:246
translate russian rjwhitneywarning_9ba477c1:

    # pc "Okay, I'm looking for it."
    pc "Ладно, я ищу."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney14.rpy:249
translate russian rjwhitneywarning_10d5b864:

    # pc "I think I found it. Box full of baggies."
    pc "Кажется, я нашел. Коробка, полная пакетиков."

